{"tid":1588313,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"約人睇車有啲人真係好撚on9.","createTime":"2019-09-22T18:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:47:29.000Z","uid":71770,"like":164,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb560cc76ff4d0af043579c1e07f3171a53dd06","tid":1588313,"uid":71770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"小弟新牌,揸咗3年到, 咁早2年幾考到車牌就買咗架二手gk5, 上手0字我1字.. 最近覺得好悶想換架新車.<br />\n<br />\n睇車前買家問我係咪車行? 我話私人放放心. 今日出到黎個買家搵咗個熟車嘅人睇. 例牌搵電筒照呀, 睇吓個籠呀, 係車場兜吓試車咁.<br />\n<br />\n之後車check車條友話條鈴花咗喎, 頭cover 條邊咁粗嘅?撞過黎呀? 頭bumper 呢到又有啲花, 應該係撞過呢面呀?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我話大佬條路有石仔架嘛 (其實甩油好細撻), 我深色車,佢唔講我都唔知花咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />況且我又冇扣過ncb, 你話我撞過, 你睇啱嘅話咪上架驗囉.<br />\n<br />\n之後我再補充, 我揸得小, &quot;收&quot; 返黎時係10000 頭km, 依家都係未夠20000. 條友就打斷我問..<br />\n<br />\n點解你用個&quot;收&quot;字, 仲話唔係車行?  我嗰時冇當場爆佢我已經覺得自己好好老脾.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走咗之後仲keep 住whatsapp 問呢樣嗰樣. on99.<br />\n<br />\ndllm, 出新車時trade in好過, 啲撚屌又要驚又要買二手. 麻撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edb2b265f2011e26f3e0c0d7817c90f3115b717","tid":1588313,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"59e924d2e87b5a548ed0fac0d7b7b2d940eb6764","tid":1588313,"uid":2419,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"咁撚講究死去買新車啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c557a938bdaebe487c7b1ec6fddf7bc1a908e001","tid":1588313,"uid":71770,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"59e924d2e87b5a548ed0fac0d7b7b2d940eb6764","tid":1588313,"uid":2419,"like":63